name: Jobinday
overview:
Jobinday is a job search engine designed to deliver a unique customer experience on mobile phones , tablets and computers.

Jobinday crawls the web every day to retrieve thousand of job opportunities coming from major job boards and companies.

Jobinday interface is natively designed to be used on android smartphones or iphone ,android tablets , ipad and computers running various operating systems.

Jobinday implements responsive design technology so that the information is displayed by taking into account screen resolution and screen orientation providing a unified and comfortable user experience.

Jobseekers can used various criterions to search jobs database : search by keyword , by industry , by town or state.

Search filters can be combined and saved as job alerts received by email daily.

Job offers are also published in realtime on social networks through dedicated pages/accounts on facebook,twitter and pinterest.

The service was born in France and is planned to be extended to several european countries and U.S soon.
